WEBVTT

00:00:00.414 --> 00:00:10.481
Over Vegas, Father. I just saw a glimpse of Vegas. Are these all on the same day?

00:00:10.482 --> 00:00:23.756
I pray over Las Vegas, Lord. It is interesting; I just saw a glimpse of New Orleans, Bourbon Street.

00:00:23.758 --> 00:00:43.159
It is an attack simultaneously when people are distracted with much drinking in these areas, with intoxication on these streets that I'm seeing.

00:00:43.160 --> 00:00:48.810
There are people that are very intoxicated; their senses are not alerted for what's happening.

00:00:48.811 --> 00:01:04.347
These areas are picked: the bars. It's not as strong in New Orleans as Tennessee and Nevada, as Nashville and Las Vegas.

00:01:04.348 --> 00:01:11.044
The party scene—there's something about New Orleans, but it's not as strong as what I see about these two places.

00:01:11.045 --> 00:01:23.757
There's something more. It's like one and many, but I would say New Orleans is darkest.

00:01:23.758 --> 00:01:34.315
But there's just one man and many. It's a mass plan; there's more than just these two.

00:01:34.316 --> 00:01:40.239
The Lord says there's more than just these two. He's given me a glimpse into these two, though.

00:01:40.240 --> 00:01:44.051
Father, there's more. Now where? But You just want me to pray over this.

00:01:44.052 --> 00:01:55.775
The city was New Orleans, and it was interesting because I only saw one individual in New Orleans. Whenever it spread, the New Orleans thing was not as hot.

00:01:55.776 --> 00:02:06.610
I want to say the point in the vision was not as intense to be concerned about that as much as what I saw in Nashville, Tennessee.

00:02:06.611 --> 00:02:13.393
Whenever I saw Nashville, Tennessee and was interceding for Nashville, it was a very strong Holy Spirit check.

00:02:13.394 --> 00:02:21.530
It's like there's something there. And then I saw a major event taking place in Nashville. Then I saw in Las Vegas.

00:02:21.531 --> 00:02:39.359
And what I thought was really interesting was it was all Middle Eastern men—like terrorist Al-Qaeda or ISIS—that's who it was.

00:02:39.360 --> 00:02:54.083
They were attacking bar areas, places that they thought were unholy, which Christians should too, but places that they thought the infidels were.

00:02:54.084 --> 00:03:05.992
It was a place of even a blasphemous sin: a bar, getting drunk, doing things like dancing or being immoral in these cities.

00:03:05.993 --> 00:03:13.742
That's all I was shown, and the vision was like those bar lights on the signs and the windows.

00:03:13.743 --> 00:03:30.438
In the vision, people were being hurt in Nashville in those areas because of the bars, and I was seeing honky-tonk dancing and stuff.

00:03:30.439 --> 00:03:35.963
Then I saw people in Las Vegas on the Strip and things happening there.

00:03:35.964 --> 00:03:42.727
That's what the Lord showed me: this is a planned thing and it would happen at the same time.

00:03:42.728 --> 00:03:59.511
It was a multi-event that would happen all in one night, like a "boom boom boom."The Lord also showed me terrorist attacks starting to try to take place in Europe. I saw terrorist attacks in Europe.

00:03:59.512 --> 00:04:17.120
I saw terrorist attacks coming out of Toronto, and I saw terrorist attacks coming into Pennsylvania and New York in very strong terrorist activities trying to take place and shake the world.

